<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink386">
<l>puṉkaṇ yāṉaiyoṭu pulivaḻaṅ katta</l>
<l>naynta kātalaṟ puṇarntuceṉ ṟaṉaḷē</l>
<l>neṭuñcuvar nalliṉ maruṇṭa</l>
<l>viṭumpai yuṟuviniṉ kaṭuñcūṉ makaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O woman, who has experienced grief, </l>
<l>bewildered in the good house behind the high walls, </l>
<l>your first-born daughter, has united with [her] beloved friend, </l>
<l>and has gone off through paths, </l>
<l> where tigers with small-eyed elephants roam.  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
